build.pyw  —  QiGor Wallpaper Manager
Build tool: PyInstaller → .exe, GitHub release upload, git source sync.

Place this file in the project root (same folder as qigor_wallpaper_manager.pyw).
Expected layout:
  qigor_wallpaper/
    build.pyw                       ← this file
    qigor_wallpaper_manager.pyw     ← entry point
    qigor_wallpaper_manager.ico     ← icon (generated by build tool)
    app/                            ← Python package
    assets/                         ← images

GitHub release structure (standard Python project pattern):
  frankksutta/qigor-wallpaper-manager
    ├── Source code (git push)
    └── Releases
          └── latest tag
                └── QiGor_Wallpaper_Manager.exe   ← release asset
"""
